Responsibilities
JOB DESCRIPTION :Maintain and develop good relationship with customers.Must act as a bridge between the company and its current market and future markets.Display efficiency in gathering market and customer info to enable negotiations regarding variations in prices, delivery and customer specifications to their managers.Help management in forthcoming products and discuss on special promotions.Review their own performance and aim at exceeding their targets.Record sales and order information and report the same to the sales department.Provide accurate feedback on future buying trends to their respective employers. REQUIREMENTS : MaleAge 22-28 years old.Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree in Industrial Engineering, Engineering (Chemical), or other Engineering fields.English and Mandarin Ability will be advantageFresh graduates are welcome to apply, or maximum 2 years experiences in Sales & Marketing.Applicants must be willing to work in Jl. Kapuk Kamal No. 19,Jakarta Utara. Interested applicants may send in their applications with the resume and most recent photograph via email to the following:HUMAN RESOURCE DEPARTMENTJl. Kapuk Kamal No.19 Jakarta UtaraorEmail address : hrd-jkt@chemstationasia.comSubject : Sales ExecutiveOnly shortlisted candidate will be notified.
